org.json.stream

Interface StructureIdentifier


  • public interface StructureIdentifier
    Holds an identifier that can be used to create a JSON Pointer expression. See RFC 6901 for details of JSON Pointer.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String getIdentifier()
      Returns an identifier fragment for this structure.

    • Method Detail

      • getIdentifier

        java.lang.String getIdentifier()
        Returns an identifier fragment for this structure. This fragment can then be used to construct a JSON Pointer value.
        Returns:
        an identifier fragment for the current structure, as a String
        See Also:
        JSONPointerUtils.toJSONPointer(Iterable)
